      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and performance for its next owner. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept strictly smoke-free. The seating surfaces are supple with no rips or thinning, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or sun damage. All interior electronics, including the touchscreen interface, heated seats, and premium audio system, are fully functional. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no unusual noises or leaks. I have maintained a rigorous service schedule, including oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent brake pad replacement. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. Included with the sale are two sets of keys and a comprehensive folder of maintenance records to ensure total transparency. This is a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
